page.title: 11LOCAL PEOPLE OF WITLEY
page.content: {Doctor Wilks}has worked at the surgery for 3 years. There are 3 doctors and 1 part timer. Doctor Wilks travels 3 miles to see patients. The surgery has been in Witley since 1965. Doctor Wilks has 2450 patients. The doctors that work there, own the surgery. Doctor Wilks writes out 350 prescriptions a month and 85 a week. {Mr.Weaire,Witley Dentist. Mr.Weaire enjoys his job. He has 4 people working for him. He has been a dentist for 24 years and he lives in Witley. He has had one famous person make an appointment,it was Gloria Hunniford. In 1971 and 1972{Charles Palmer}wrote 'The History of Witley'and 'Witley Lives'.The books give an in depth study of all aspects of the locality.
